      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is currently in good running order, making it a reliable choice for daily transportation. The engine and transmission are functional and have been regularly serviced, though the car does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches and minor dings. Inside, the upholstery shows some wear, and while all major systems work, some minor interior components may require attention. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
